<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>It's A Great Stay At The Olimpo Court Hotel There have been some changes at the Olimpo Court Hotel, but the professionalism and services still remain the same. They were quite knowledgeable about directions if you are looking to travel outside San Juan, e.g., like the famous Hato Rey Mall, quite beautiful and breath-taking, or to Old San Juan, where you can go during the day and shop for Coach or Dooney  Burke Bags, just to name a few. Directions were great. The staff was very polite, knowledgeable and professional, yet gracious. Exclusively nice and accommodating. The room was always clean, the beds were always made nice and clean, plenty of towels, small kitchen was great and the microwave was quite accommodating. All in all, my son and I enjoyed our stay there, and if I ever go back to San Juan......I'M GOING TO THE OLIMPO COURT HOTEL.....You don't need expensive and costly to enjoy your stay.......the Olimpo Court Hotel was great........terrace was breathtaking.......stores around the corner......clean towels........great service.....Day/Night Clerks were great and informative.......LOVED IT ALL......Brought back many memories.........IN LOVE WITH THE OLIMPO COURT HOTEL...... 
